mlogic.algos.struct

Class ChainedHashTable<Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>,Value>

  • java.lang.Object
    • mlogic.algos.struct.ChainedHashTable<Key,Value>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HashTable<Key,Value>

    public class ChainedHashTable<Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>,Value>
extends java.lang.Object
implements HashTable<Key,Value>
    Hash table organized as an array of buckets. Each bucket is a linked list containing all the items that hash to the same value.
    Author:
    Rajaram G
